        "Target": "\u30D3\u30B7\u30E5\u30C6\u30F3\u30B4\uFF11\u982D\u3068\u30AA\u30ED\u30DF\u30C9\u30ED\uFF11\u982D\u306E\u72E9\u731F",
        "Fail": "\u5831\u916C\u91D1\u30BC\u30ED\r\n\u30BF\u30A4\u30E0\u30A2\u30C3\u30D7"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Tail to Tail",
        "Client": "Well-informed Man",
        "Description": "Both Bishaten and Almudron are known\r\nfor using their powerful tails when they\r\nattack. I\u0027m collecting information on\r\nthese monsters. Could you possibly\r\nassist me? I need to ascertain which\r\ntail is stronger. The one like a fist,\r\nor the one like a whip?",
        "Target": "Hunt a Bishaten and an Almudron",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Queue \u00E0 queue",
        "Client": "Homme bien inform\u00E9",
        "Description": "Le Bishaten et l\u0027Almudron utilisent\r\ntous les deux leur puissante queue\r\npour attaquer. Je veux en apprendre\r\nplus sur ces monstres, pourrais-tu\r\nm\u0027aider ? J\u0027aimerais savoir quelle\r\nest la meilleure queue ? Celle qui\r\nressemble \u00E0 un poing ou \u00E0 un fouet ?",
        "Target": "Chasser un Bishaten et un Almudron",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Coda a coda",
        "Client": "Uomo ben informato",
        "Description": "Sia il Bishaten sia l\u0027Almudron\r\nusano le loro potenti code per\r\nattaccare. Sto raccogliendo\r\ninformazioni su questi mostri.\r\nPotresti aiutarmi? Devo\r\ncapire quale coda \u00E8 pi\u00F9 forte:\r\nquella a pugno o a frusta?",
        "Target": "Caccia un Bishaten e un Almudron",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Schwanz an Schwanz",
        "Client": "Gut informierter Mann",
        "Description": "Sowohl Bishaten als auch Almudron sind\r\ndaf\u00FCr bekannt, ihre kr\u00E4ftigen Schw\u00E4nze\r\nbeim Angreifen einzusetzen. Ich sammle\r\nDaten zu diesen Monstern. W\u00FCrdest du\r\nmir helfen? Ich muss pr\u00FCfen, welcher\r\nSchwanz st\u00E4rker ist: der faust\u00E4hnliche\r\noder der peitschenartige?",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Bishaten und\r\neinen Almudron.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Cara a cara, cola a cola",
        "Client": "Tipo bien informado",
        "Description": "Los Bishaten y los Almudron\r\nusan sus poderosas colas para\r\natacar, y estoy reuniendo\r\ndatos de ambos monstruos.\r\n\u00BFMe ayudas? Quiero saber\r\ncu\u00E1l de los dos tiene la cola\r\nm\u00E1s fuerte.",
        "Target": "Caza un Bishaten y un Almudron",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0425\u0432\u043E\u0441\u0442\u043E\u043C \u043A \u0445\u0432\u043E\u0441\u0442\u0443",
        "Client": "\u0418\u043D\u0444\u043E\u0440\u043C\u0438\u0440\u043E\u0432\u0430\u043D\u043D\u044B\u0439 \u0447\u0435\u043B\u043E\u0432\u0435\u043A",
        "Description": "\u0418 \u0411\u0438\u0441\u044F\u0442\u044D\u043D, \u0438 \u0410\u043B\u043C\u0443\u0434\u0440\u043E\u043D \u0438\u0437\u0432\u0435\u0441\u0442\u043D\u044B\r\n\u0442\u0435\u043C, \u0447\u0442\u043E \u0431\u044C\u044E\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0430\u0433\u043E\u0432\r\n\u0445\u0432\u043E\u0441\u0442\u0430\u043C\u0438. \u042F \u0438\u0437\u0443\u0447\u0430\u044E \u044D\u0442\u0438\u0445\r\n\u043C\u043E\u043D\u0441\u0442\u0440\u043E\u0432. \u0422\u044B \u043C\u043E\u0436\u0435\u0448\u044C \u043C\u043D\u0435\r\n\u043F\u043E\u043C\u043E\u0447\u044C? \u042F \u0445\u043E\u0447\u0443 \u0443\u0437\u043D\u0430\u0442\u044C, \u0447\u0435\u0439\r\n\u0445\u0432\u043E\u0441\u0442 \u0441\u0438\u043B\u044C\u043D\u0435\u0435 \u2014 \u0442\u043E\u0442, \u0447\u0442\u043E \u043A\u0430\u043A\r\n\u043A\u0443\u043B\u0430\u043A, \u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0442\u043E\u0442, \u0447\u0442\u043E \u043A\u0430\u043A \u043F\u043B\u0435\u0442\u044C?",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u0411\u0438\u0441\u044F\u0442\u044D\u043D\u0430 \u0438 \u0410\u043B\u043C\u0443\u0434\u0440\u043E\u043D\u0430",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POL",
        "Name": "Ogon do ogona",
        "Client": "Poinformowany m\u0119\u017Cczyzna",
        "Description": "Bishaten i Almudron znane s\u0105\r\nz u\u017Cywania swych pot\u0119\u017Cnych ogon\u00F3w\r\ndo atakowania. Zbieram informacje\r\nna ich temat. Pomo\u017Cesz mi?\r\nMusz\u0119 ustali\u0107, kt\u00F3ry ogon jest\r\nsilniejszy \u2013 ten podobny do\r\npi\u0119\u015Bci czy ten w kszta\u0142cie bata.",
